lds of common interest, said the DGSN-DGST in a statement.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdellatif_Hammouchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abdellatif Hammouchi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdellatif_Hammouchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdellatif_Hammouchi\"}, {\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998121893, \"rank\": 1.8780335272259113e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999856716293536, \"rank\": 1.3315169208237549e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999856716293536, \"rank\": 1.3315169208237549e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a working visit\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the official invitation\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"talks\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Police\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"Internal Security\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"Director-General\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"External Security\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"France\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 988}, {\