gram\": \"various security fields\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A special focus was laid on the development of proactive mechanisms for risk assessment and data exchange, the perspective being joint action in securing the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris, the statement noted.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998121893, \"rank\": 1.8780335272259113e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A special focus\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"proactive mechanisms\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"risk assessment\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"data exchange\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the perspective\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"joint action\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In tribute to the exemplary Morocco-France cooperation in various security areas, the DGSN-DGST Director-General was awarded the Gold Medal of Honor by the French National Police, in recognition of his efforts to consolidate and bolster security cooperation.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Police_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9999999974052116, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French National Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Police_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Police_(France)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the exemplary Morocco-France cooperation\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"various security areas\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the DGSN-DGST Director-General\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gold Medal\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"Honor\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"his efforts\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"security cooperation\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The visit provided an opportunity for the French and Moroccan sides to discuss ways to further strengthen their cooperation in a wide range of areas to combat transnational crime, especially smuggling of narcotic drugs and psychotropic substances, illegal migration and human trafficking networks, as well as practical mechanisms for cooperation in implementing joint security measures and operations.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999856716293536, \"rank\": 1.3315169208237549e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.9999999036267628, \"rank\": 9.637320554676497e-08, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The visit\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"their cooperation\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"a wide range\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"transnational crime\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"especially smuggling\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"narcotic drugs\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"psychotropic substances\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"illegal migration\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"human trafficking networks\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"practical mechanisms\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"cooperation\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"joint security measures\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"operations\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The visit attests to the importance of boosting security cooperation between Morocco and France, which share many bilateral action and coordination programs and face common security challenges, the statement added.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2783, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.715075869576477e-19, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}, {\"begin\": 2795, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9991599417898005, \"rank\": 0.0008283131377954978, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The visit\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"security cooperation\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"many bilateral action and coordination programs\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"common security challenges\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 291